documentation.desc: Determines whether there are mouse-button or keyboard messages in the calling thread's message queue.

apidoc.return: If the queue contains one or more new mouse-button or keyboard messages, the return value is nonzero. If there are no new mouse-button or keyboard messages in the queue, the return value is zero.
